msgstr "ユーザーアカウントのデフォルト設定、フィールド、登録条件、eメールのメッセージを構成。"

msgid ""
"Too many failed login attempts from your IP address. This IP address "
"is temporarily blocked. Try again later or <a href=\":url\">request a "
